<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,530,1625,1651]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="103">Pseudobiceros luteomarginatus</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Yeri" box="[546,836,1625,1651]" pageId="2" pageNumber="117" refString="Yeri, M. &amp; Kaburaki, T. (1918) Description of some Japanese Polyclad Turbellaria. Journal of the College of Science, Tokyo Imperial University, 39 (9), 1 - 54." type="journal article" year="1918">
Yeri &amp; Kaburaki, 
